sub_title: Training Coordinator | Mid Office & Back office administration | Project Support | Policy
summary:
Professional with extensive experience in planning and coordination with the past 6 years in the areas of education & training, onboarding & recruitment/sales.

Highly organised & self-motivated with strong communication & problem-solving skills, always striving to deliver excellent work & provide excellent service. Being inquisitive I believe there is always something to learn. 

Bilingual in English and Chinese/Mandarin, and competent in Dutch.
